flavor_text_entries.flavor_text:
It makes fur balls that crackle
with static electricity. It stores
them with berries in tree holes.

It makes electricity with pouches
in its cheeks and shoots charges
from its tail. It lives atop trees.

A pair may be seen rubbing their
cheek pouches together in an
effort to share stored electricity.

It’s one of the kinds of Pokémon 
with electric cheek pouches.
It shoots charges from its tail.

せいでんきが　たまって　パチパチする
けだまを　だいこうぶつの　きのみと
いっしょに　みきの　あなに　かくす。

정전기가 모여 톡톡 튀는 솜털을
자신이 좋아하는 나무열매와 함께
나무줄기의 구멍에 숨긴다.

Il roule des boules de poils pleines d’électricité
statique et les range dans des souches avec des
Baies.

Es bildet ein Fellknäuel, der vor statischer Energie
knistert. Es speichert die Energie in Bäumen.

Crea bolas de pelo que crepitan con electricidad
estática. Las almacena en agujeros de árboles.

Forma delle palle di pelo cariche elettrostaticamente
e le conserva negli alberi insieme alle bacche.

It makes fur balls that crackle with static electricity.
It stores them with berries in tree holes.

静電気が　たまって　パチパチする
毛玉を　大好物の　木の実と　一緒に
幹の　穴に　隠す。

たまった　でんきを　わけあたえようと
ほほぶくろを　こすりあわせる
パチリスを　みかけることも　ある。

모인 전기를 나눠주려고
뺨의 주머니를 서로 비비는
파치리스가 발견되기도 한다.

Il arrive que deux Pachirisu se frottent les joues pour
partager l’électricité qu’ils ont accumulée.

Um gespeicherte Elektrizität zu teilen, reiben zwei
von ihnen ihre Backentaschen aneinander.

A veces se ve a dos frotándose las bolsas de las
mejillas para compartir electricidad almacenada.

Talvolta due esemplari si sfregano le guance per
condividere l’elettricità immagazzinata.

A pair may be seen rubbing their cheek pouches
together in an effort to share stored electricity.

パチリスを　見かけることも　ある。
